- Hudson might be better for Maven integration since it is part of Oracle and Sonatype?

- Basic CI maturity
  Phase 1 -> no build server
  Phase 2 -> nightly builds (no automated testing)
  Phase 3 -> nightly builds and basic automated tests
  Phase 4 -> automated code quality and coverage metrics available
  Phase 5 -> Test Driven Development practices
  Phase 6 -> Acceptance Test Driven Development and Behavior Driven Development practices
  Phase 7 -> with automated unit, integration, and acceptance tests, Automated Deployment can be practiced.
